@841    = ~USE MAGIC DEVICE (Cha; Trained Only; Bard, Rogue Only):

This skill allows a bard or rogue to use items normally forbidden to them. If the character's skill is greater than or equal to the threshold stated in an item's description, the character can use that item even if they do not meet its class, race, alignment, or ability score requirements. The threshold depends on the base price of the item and other factors.

Wands and scrolls are an exception; if the character cannot use them normally, rather than using the threshold system as above, they must roll a check with this skill. If the character fails to activate the item, that charge is destroyed and the user takes 1-6 points of magical damage per level of the effect they were attempting to invoke.~
